{"tid":2076048,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"幸福的中國農民 - 李純恩","createTime":"2020-06-23T08:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T09:08:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f82c18fd70800765c5312a53f10d1f6f1ffd74b2","tid":2076048,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9/daily/article/20200623/20942235/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200623%2F20942235%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JW%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=4e7ab2a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200623%2F20942235%2F&h=8961b47b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9/daily/article/20200623/20942235/</a><br />\n<br />\n幸福的中國農民 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200623/large/1592811400_ad62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200623%2Flarge%2F1592811400_ad62.jpg&h=8905cdad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n朋友發了。。。。。熱之中的美國人民」。<br />\n<br />\n這自然是幸福感滿溢的中國人民在潤他們以為水深火熱的美國人民，覺得天下之大，只有中國人生活在天堂，北朝鮮最多在半空，其他萬惡的資本主義國家的人，都活在地獄裏。這條標語刷在農民家的外牆上，戶主別說美國，可能上海都沒去過，平日追求「老婆孩子熱炕頭」，晚晚看央視《新聞聯播》，幸福得要命了。<br />\n<br />\n中國只要有這樣的農民，。。。。。。所以領導人必須一開口就像農民那樣說話。<br />\n<br />\n但你也不要以為只有中國領導人討好農民，美國領導人也一樣，不然特朗普就不會叫習大大買那麼多美國大豆了對不對，特朗普如果得習大大之助，幫美國農民賣出了大豆，美國農民就「擼起袖子」把選票投給他了。中國農民以為美國農民水深火熱，美國農民說不定也以為中國農民水深火熱，誰比誰更有腦呀！ <br />\n<br />\n李純恩<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"f22ae7ce849cb249c80b903f9b4571c092f99937","tid":2076048,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}